&gt; In order to preserve any existing flags, shouldn&#39;t this be more like:<br>
&gt;   int prev;<br>
&gt;   if ((-1 == (prev =  fcntl(root, F_GETFD, 0)) ||<br>
&gt;       (-1 == fcntl(root, F_SETFD, FD_CLOEXEC | prev)))<br>
